    </div>

    <!-- Description -->
    <p class="text-center text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 text-gray-700">
      We provide the Best online PDR training available. New techs to seasoned veterans will find tips and tricks and everything necessary to advance as a PDR technician. We teach the skills to make students highly marketable and proficient in all aspects of Paintless dent repair.
    </p>

    <!-- Contact info -->
